{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/new_InLine_Discord_Image.png?t=1737739655\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SPELLHACK!! </strong>is a survival deckbuilder that features fast-paced, arcadey combat and a surreal 1980s setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During the <strong>day</strong>, you have 12 hours to spend improving your Spelldrive and collecting new Technospells. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At <strong>night</strong>, the Summoned Beasts descend upon you. You'll need to think fast to survive  12 hours of nighttime before the next day arrives!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/final_nite_gif.gif?t=1737739655\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SPELLHACK!! Floppy Disk Contents:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <strong>Story Mode</strong> to ease into the pace and mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <strong>Challenge Mode with 5 levels</strong>  to really test your skills!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>150+ Technospells</strong> to collect and install </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>50+ Summoned Beasts</strong> to repel </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A huge variety of <strong>items</strong> to collect and <strong>events</strong> to encounter </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Graphics so good you'll forget <strong>its just a game</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Characters with <strong>no</strong> ulterior motives! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And <strong>more</strong>!!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/daytime_gif_fo